{"tid":210214,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[罪大] A7ii+福仔","createTime":"2017-04-20T18:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T11:29:55.000Z","uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d39259ac1e3f96f38f0ce4fd93b8d45822bb9380","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"小弟目前有枝2470z <br />\n屎忽痕想買支Voigtlander 40mm 1.4 做鏡頭蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底買唔買好 有無啲買左嘅巴打可以share 下啲sample黎睇下<br />\n同埋係邊到搵到??肥花?天祥?星際? <br />\n仲有都想請教下adaptor點買 都係買返福仔個adaptor?<br />\n定係我見啲人會係淘寶買adaptor平好多<br />\n其實影響大唔大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係唔識 有無巴打可以教下路<br />\n同埋呢枝鏡應該賣2800-3000有無巴打知價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0f065292c9393c8556e03d8f114c6d210a4341","tid":210214,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"平，做工好<br />\n但散景太二線，未必啱你心水<br />\n其實$2500仲有好多選擇"},{"pid":"4b471a8353642297bff29a1a610a3266efd7dace","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平，做工好<br />\n但散景太二線，未必啱你心水<br />\n其實$2500仲有好多選擇</blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩推介？第一次接觸手動鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係驚買返黎舖塵"},{"pid":"167c4a70a7d3cd45a3b7e17239f644688bf3fe8a","tid":210214,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bfe79fc590beae43ad509444a15e174bb47504cb","tid":210214,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"鏡頭蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260d3f6bdf34f2d56e15d474dca4da439972e009","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"