ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平，做工好<br />\n但散景太二線，未必啱你心水<br />\n其實$2500仲有好多選擇</blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩推介？第一次接觸手動鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係驚買返黎舖塵</blockquote><br />\n推介下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買G45 + 天工3啦<br />\n自動又得 手動又得<br />\n<br />\n自從買左支G45<br />\n40 .4 封左塵"},{"pid":"9d38898de6ffc0905e50347f247ba7019258939b","tid":210214,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>35 1.4?</blockquote><br />\n幾錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲要買埋adapter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n35 CP值冇 40咁高<br />\n<br />\n諗下你想要SC 定 MC <br />\n利申 有支40 .4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你堅持買既<br />\n我有支40.4 MC + Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter 放 $4200<br />\n買左3個月, 淨係去大阪用左次"},{"pid":"5914817389752ea2bbedcd163e10bf6190685ce3","tid":210214,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"Contax G 35/2 同 Leica M summicron-c 40mm f2 都靚過日福40/1.4"},{"pid":"54b523624f936ee7f50b34f3bdd3d82dae37b9f5","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>35 1.4?</blockquote><br />\n幾錢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲要買埋adapter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n35 CP值冇 40咁高<br />\n<br />\n諗下你想要SC 定 MC <br />\n利申 有支40 .4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你堅持買既<br />\n我有支40.4 MC + Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter 放 $4200<br />\n買左3個月, 淨係去大阪用左次</blockquote><br />\n影彩色 應該要MC啦 我係想知除左原廠但adapter 有無其他選擇 因為好似有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07503b5062f8f88592b324c9251d45d428d95dca","tid":210214,"uid":48838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位"},{"pid":"683b415d2333b0d8cc7c9921f02b958899aaa042","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位</blockquote><br />\n其實點解一個adapter都咁貴 好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c91ca6d930a05af31c63010929552f371b8a1dd","tid":210214,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位</blockquote><br />\n其實點解一個adapter都咁貴 好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做工 靚 close focus 有用<br />\n當然同樣價錢可以買天工<br />\n不過用料兩回事<br />\n<br />\n玩得M鏡 梗係要手動 同用原裝野啦"},{"pid":"70ffe7acc377cc73234779b066ecacc6ed59619e","tid":210214,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位</blockquote><br />\n其實點解一個adapter都咁貴 好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做工 靚 close focus 有用<br />\n當然同樣價錢可以買天工<br />\n不過用料兩回事<br />\n<br />\n玩得M鏡 梗係要手動 同用原裝野啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過咁多個adapter, Voigtlander 做工最好，Metabones都同佢差好遠<br />\n而且close focus好有用，M鏡個shortest focus distance枝枝都0.7m起跳，基本上嘢食都影唔到，但用close focus adapter可以將個shortest focus distance 縮短差唔多一倍，影近嘢都得<br />\n<br />\nVM40係我第一枝手動鏡，CP好高，不過成像好有個性，未必個個like，但係用嚟做入門手動鏡好得<br />\nSharpness 夠，立體感OK，又有1.4光圈"},{"pid":"24c07dc11c6b8e12140b3bf010dc8fbac9bf005b","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位</blockquote><br />\n其實點解一個adapter都咁貴 好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做工 靚 close focus 有用<br />\n當然同樣價錢可以買天工<br />\n不過用料兩回事<br />\n<br />\n玩得M鏡 梗係要手動 同用原裝野啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用過咁多個adapter, Voigtlander 做工最好，Metabones都同佢差好遠<br />\n而且close focus好有用，M鏡個shortest focus distance枝枝都0.7m起跳，基本上嘢食都影唔到，但用close focus adapter可以將個shortest focus distance 縮短差唔多一倍，影近嘢都得<br />\n<br />\nVM40係我第一枝手動鏡，CP好高，不過成像好有個性，未必個個like，但係用嚟做入門手動鏡好得<br />\nSharpness 夠，立體感OK，又有1.4光圈</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以話我知close focus adaptor+VM40埋單幾錢 <br />\n同埋係邊到入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac92c9b778c2db4979f595d6ea6fbc3fadbc1826","tid":210214,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Voigtlander VM-E Close Focus Adapter<br />\n<br />\n一步到位</blockquote><br />\n其實點解一個adapter都咁貴 好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做工 靚 close focus 有用<br />\n當然同樣價錢可以買天工<br />\n不過用料兩回事<br />\n<br />\n玩得M鏡 梗係要手動 同用原裝野啦</blockquote><br />\n咩係天工 小弟不材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed34021100e57718cea7ced1edc7c24902d330f2","tid":210214,"uid":23332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"CP值高到不得了，用左三年都長期插住<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F48N8KN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF48N8KN.jpg&h=a6ea72fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2183F1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2183F1B.jpg&h=a7120b6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"147982aa037ca28e139b6f39dcc06af15d94a20c","tid":210214,"uid":23332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔係太研究，作為興趣既話買個幾十蚊adapter 已經夠，淘寶close focus 果款都係百幾二百<br />\n睇自己銀包做人啦。<br />\n<br />\nVm40 上左a7之後完全將無反既輕便既優點發揮曬出黎，買得vm40都係為左個1.4 ，陰天會發揮得好啲，全開啲散景比較有特色，我通常長期都係用1.4-2.8<br />\n而我就覺得二千中呢個價錢呢支野既質素真係無得挑剔"},{"pid":"d5c2fde950715be8d2363cf607b43efd276e7ff8","tid":210214,"uid":14885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"神力環淘寶就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}